            <title>[PIG-3777] Pig 12.0 Documentation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3777</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think the example for SAMPLE is wrong&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this example, a scalar expression is used (it will sample approximately 1000 records from the input).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a = load &apos;a.txt&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
b = group a all;&lt;br/&gt;
c = foreach b generate COUNT(a) as num_rows;&lt;br/&gt;
e = sample d 1000/num_rows;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is no relation d and I get a &quot;Projected field &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;num_rows&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; does not exist in schema&quot; error, I think it need to be &lt;br/&gt;
e = sample a 1000/c.numrows&lt;/p&gt;</description>
